{"type":"message","id":"9fcc173e","parentId":"3f1aad0b","timestamp":"2026-03-02T10:33:43.119Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0d5d0996-0ac8-46ce-95b1-f011cd726ada Polymarket市场扫描] 执行 Polymarket 模拟交易扫描:\n\n1. 运行 cd /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/polymarket-paper && python3 cli.py scan\n2. 如果有交易机会，发送详细报告给胡总\n3. 报告格式：市场名称、概率、推荐交易方向、策略类型\n\n注意：仅分析不执行真实交易，用中文回复\nCurrent time: Monday, March 2nd, 2026 — 10:33 AM (UTC)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772447623112}}
